title: Is A Hot Dog A Sandwich? ft. The Philosopher, Dr. Calvin Normore (Part 2)
description:
What differences make a difference? Why hot dogs? Who am I? Today, we're joined by philosopher Calvin Normore in part 2 of our series that attempts to answer the question on all of our minds: is a hot dog a sandwich?
